{"tid":1226756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中區龍和道及添華道一帶意外遺失一支伸縮警、一部警察通訊器及一瓶胡椒噴劑。","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:11:29.000Z","uid":226864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f17a24a2cf9c79de7512719adaf7493efd18a9","tid":1226756,"uid":226864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:06:43.000Z","msg":"3名隸屬新界南總區的警務人員於周三（12日）下午的反修訂《逃犯條例》警民衝突中，於中區龍和道及添華道一帶執勤期間分別意外遺失一支伸縮警棍、一部警察通訊器及一瓶胡椒噴劑。<br />\n<br />\n警方接獲遺失器材的報告後，立即展開調查及到現場搜尋，暫未有發現。案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由有關人員所屬單位跟進調查。有關警察通訊器已停用及失效。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲有關物品，應立即交到就近的警署，或致電3661 1222、3661 1233或3660 1261與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格的規定。警方會繼續就有關事件作出跟進。<br />\n還你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1523424/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1523424%2F&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgLzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=84aad61b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1523424%2F&h=3e906013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1523424/</a>"},{"pid":"b55401ce7c8f6fb2319099e48d068e4c37c766aa","tid":1226756,"uid":226864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc38a344a4352540b2478ea6d5f156325df302b2","tid":1226756,"uid":226864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f72a7f8b78e09914cf437b882783220ab6fbfb16","tid":1226756,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"係咪想屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9011c8d85a44297ff01d53810d54c83ec8acde5b","tid":122675